node.text:
Good morning! 😍 This stone home is located at 13360 W 167th Street in Homer Glen, Illinois and is situated on 4.5 acres of land.

It was built in 2012 and features approximately 15,000 square feet of living space with 5 bedrooms, 6 full and 3 half bathrooms, 2-story foyer with staircase, elevator, 2-story great room, wet bar, formal dining room, gourmet kitchen, breakfast room, office, lower level family room with bistro area & wet bar, billiards room, collector’s room, catering kitchen, indoor spa, home theater, gym, 10+ car garage and more.

Outdoor features include a gated entrance, fountain, porte-cochere, terraces, kitchen/BBQ and a resort-style pool complete with spa and diving board.

🌍 13360 W 167th Street, Homer Glen, Illinois 🏠 15,000 Square Feet 🛏 5 Bedrooms 🛁 9 Bathrooms 💰 $5,999,999
